song.title: You Just Can't Keep Me Down
song.info:
"This one I did in three days right before Breakpoint, just because I wanted to release something in the MP3 compo as well. I like some elements of it, maybe I'll do a remix of it one day. It could be a lot better anyway."
Ranked 3rd in the streaming music compo at Breakpoint 2006 held in Rundsporthalle, Bingen am Rhein, Germany from 14th to 17th April, 2006.
